      "releaseNotes": "Managing your easyJet holiday is now easier with the new holidays app experience. \n\nYou’ll now have useful hotel information at your fingertips, like check-in and check-out dates, hotel address, and quick links to our help centre. \n\nPlease keep sending us feedback and feature ideas at app.feedback.iphone@easyjet.com",
